Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:28.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone. Shiniga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:10.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that this is\Na live worldwide broadcast...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...this is only being broadcast\Nin the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first victim was the killer in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:22.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, his crime was\Nonly broadcast in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been able to deduce this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:33.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in Japan and\Nyour first victim was your guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.04,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,290)}Kira Task Force Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has found a way to obtain information\Nfrom the task force headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 141 people within\Nthe police force alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who have access to investigative\Ninformation on Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:51.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the 141 people\Nor someone close to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is definitely among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.28,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,351)}FBI Investigation of Those Involved\Nwith the Japanese Police
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:03.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On December 14, twelve FBI agents\Nentered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,December 19. Kira began using\Nprisoners to conduct tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,concerning actions\Na victim can take before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to erase all of the FBI agents...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he had to see how far he could\Ncontrol the death of his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I suspect that Kira\Nwas one of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who was being investigated by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,between the fourteenth\Nand the nineteenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.23,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,350)\fad(208,0)}An Important Witness\NNaomi Misora
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye Penber's fiancée?\NNaomi Misora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked under me on that case\Nand now she's in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was with Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might have found a clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Ndid Kira get to her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.47,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,290)}Light Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone. From now on,\Nwe'll focus our investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the people who Raye Penber\Nwas investigating while in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:14.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Director General Kitamura\Nand his family,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Detective Superintendent Yagami\Nand his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:23.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wish to place wiretaps and\Nsurveillance cameras in both households.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:28.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, are you telling me\Nthat you suspect my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:29.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.29,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,291)}Contact with Light Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:47.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira hates to lose,\Nbut most people don't like to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you came in for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami, I suspect that you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:07.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuga, is there any way that I can get\Nyou to believe that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:13.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. We'll know in time\Nif you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.50,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,372)}Kira Murders, Using a Television Station
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Four days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- our program director...\N- Our audience rating could go up sixty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- was sent these four tapes.\N- no, seventy percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A tape which predicts the killings\Nto prove that he is Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:32.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And another to send a message\Nto the people of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The news anchor,\NMr. Kazuhiko Hibima,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will die of a heart attack\Nat exactly six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible will happen\Nif we don't stop this broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:47.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira shouldn't be able to\Nkill without a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:51.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I just saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:56.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not entirely impossible that\Nhe may only need a face to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the police!\NStop this program!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a high possibility that\Nthis Kira is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we should call him\Nthe Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:15.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami. May I ask your son\Nto cooperate in this investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.98,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,356)}Light Yagami is Summoned to\NTask Force Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a good chance that this\Nis not the Kira we've known until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly the same deduction\Nas L, I mean Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:25.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we can confirm our identities by\Nshowing our Shinigami to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a code
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:37.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that only people who have the so-called\NShinigami power can understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't decode it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:45.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we should thoroughly check out\Nthe places listed in the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:49.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be sure to watch\NLight very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event that Light is Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:56.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Second Kira might try\Nto contact him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:02.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Mr. Yagami. I would like Mr. Mogi\Nto keep watch over Light's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.27,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,356)}Misa Amane Arrested Under Suspicion\Nof Being the Second Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light--! There you are--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Light's girlfriend, Misa Amane.\NPleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:13.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideki Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be good and\Nbad news to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Misa Amane has just\Nbeen taken into custody
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,under suspicion of being\Nthe Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were hairs and fibers...\Namong other things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:30.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,attached to the masking tape sealing\Nthe video tapes the Second Kira sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We discovered many matching samples\Nof evidence in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.93,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,290)}Misa Amane's Confinement
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki! What is this-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to\Nkill me immediately, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because you admit\Nto being the Second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No--! I don't know anything\Nabout the Second Kira-!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.36,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,358)}Light Yagami is Confined at\NHis Own Request
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:55.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, I told you over the phone,\Nbut I think I may be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to say that he may be Kira-?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:07:59.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you may be Kira,\Nbut that you are Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:10.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I know I probably look\Npretty bad in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but this pride,\NI'll just have to get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:20.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki! I did indeed agree to\Nbe detained and chose to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I just clearly realized\Nthat I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me out of here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:31.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two weeks worth of criminals\Nwere murdered all at once yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two People Released
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like all three of them\Nare at their limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, why are you\Nstill confining Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been fifty days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill you here\Nand then kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's crazy!\N- Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- It would be better if we ran away.\N- It's too late, Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Dad, I'm not Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:02.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...from one murderer to another,\NI'll see you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a convincing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I promised,\NI will end their confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.70,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,356)}Light Yagami Once Again is Summoned\Nto Help with the Investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Light, I will arrange things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:25.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you and I will be together 24 hours\Na day working on the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.88,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,293)}Yotsuba
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're deaths that are\Nin Yotsuba's favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking back, there have been\Nas many as thirteen such cases
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the past three months...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigation and Infiltration of Yotsuba\N- Is Kira someone from Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is Kira using Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't figured that out yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but let's investigate this with the\Nassumption that this is Kira's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's thoroughly investigate Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be sure not to act\Nout of panic or haste...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and don't take matters into\Nyour own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Taro Matsui.\NAn agent with Yoshida Productions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you like to use Misa Amane\Nin your commercials-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The eight of them that came\Nwere having a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to determine who\Nto have Kira kill for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Matsuda dies that would justify\Nthe suspicion against Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do\Nto save myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.30,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,330)}Kyosuke Higuchi Confirmed to be Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Misa-misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when they decide to put you\Nin their commercials!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dream to become Kira's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm Kira, so marry me, Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Higuchi is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.16,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,353)}The Plan to Capture Higuchi\Nis Put into Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to trick Higuchi\Nusing Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden camera show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi, this is bad. Turn on your TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So one of these people is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:56.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have a lot of proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:10:59.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he alive-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed Higuchi.\NI'm going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:17.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your car.\NPull over to the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem. Let's make the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal-?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were speeding.\NShow me your driver's license!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi ditched the motorcycle cop\Nand is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the highway patrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:40.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! It's too dangerous to\Nlet Higuchi alone any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We will proceed to capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi is now able to kill by\Nlooking at someone's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:47.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We will capture him with that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you come near me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.41,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,289)}Capture of Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:07.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi... How do you kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I write the name of someone\Nwhose face I know in that notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that person dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's one in Higuchi's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more than\Ntwo notebooks in existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:34.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't finished yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note and\Nan Inquiry Into Its Rules
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"How to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:44.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name\Nis written in this note shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"And this last sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"lf the person using the note fails
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:54.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"to consecutively write names\Nof people to be killed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:57.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"within thirteen days of each other,\Nthen the user will die..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami and Misa Amane\Nare living...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:05.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:16.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The following is the record which\Ncontains everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have investigated\Non the Kira incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you are\Nreading this message means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am no longer alive at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:32.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby leave this record\Nas my firm achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten days since\NRyuzaki's secret funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we aren't going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We now know Watari's identity,\Nbut in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't find out anything\Nabout Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Watari was actually\Nan amazing inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He created orphanages worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with the fortune he made from\Nseveral of his patents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hero! A hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:27.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't continue investigating here\Nnow that L and Watari are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:36.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can remove the entire system\Nhere by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel good about it.\NIt feels like stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've created a voice like the\None that Ryuzaki used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can act like he's still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and control the police\Nas we've been doing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will replace L? Where will we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do with the killer notebook-?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can take\Nthe role of L is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:06.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ryuzaki was killed by Kira\Nfor challenging him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel comfortable about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, it'll be tricking\Nthe people of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings,\Nbut you're the only one who can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Ryuzaki said it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be capable of succeeding L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:28.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How easy... It's no fun without Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all right. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't do anything dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:40.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like challenging Kira directly\Nto gain clues, like Ryuzaki did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That would be better and safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki may have been\Ntoo confrontational...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do about the same work\Nwith this computer and my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also possible to be L\Nfrom my room at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be difficult to do this\Nwith my mom and little sister around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be good if I could rent\Na one-room apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:12.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing suspicious about renting\Na room for my son to live on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:17.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the place he'll be renting out\Nwill be the task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:21.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is what to do\Nwith the killer notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to think too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have one of the five of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:30.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who we trust will never\Nuse the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,hide it somewhere\Nwhere no one can get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...please do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pillar of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, huh-?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:44.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avenge Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:52.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Kira's still here.\NLet's catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's have a party to\Ncelebrate Light becoming the second L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fooling around, now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our first date in a while.\NEnjoy yourself a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:25.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've already rented a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right--! We're living together--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa wins-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:34.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, against Kiyomi\Nand Mari and Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just used them to trick L, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't see them anymore, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:46.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your score finally settled with L?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:04.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't expect anything\Ninteresting anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:09.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on...
